para_trans: Government Hostel for Backward Class Girls,
Regarding administrative approval of budget for construction of hostel building at Sainath Colony, Kasba Bawda, Kolhapur.
Government of Maharashtra
Department of Social Justice and Special Assistance
Government Decision No: Sanyavi-2025 / Q.08 / Constructions
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
Mantralaya, Mumbai Yoo 032.
Date: November 13, 2025.
Read: - 1. Letter from Commissioner, Social Welfare, Pune Go to No. S.A. / Education / Construction / 04 Shawgu / Kolhapur / Nabanna / Sudha. Anda / ka-5a / 2025-26, d. 8.07.2025.
2. The High-Level Committee of Secretaries. History of the meetings on 28.10.2025.
The Government's Decisions:
The High-Level Committee of Secretaries Public Works Department in its meeting on 28.10.2025

The Government Hostel for Backward Class Girls, Sainath Colony, Kasba Bawda, Kolhapur was constructed at a cost of Rs. 9701.68 Attention / - A budget of this amount is being granted administrative approval subject to the following conditions: - a) The prototype map, layout map as well as detailed map should be started only with the approval of the architect before starting the work.
b) Work on a broad budget should be undertaken when dealing with a broad-based provision.
e) Department of Environment, Government Decision No. ENV-2013 / P.S. No.177 / T.A.1, D. Action should be taken as per the guidelines mentioned in January 10, 2014.
e) The cost of construction of the work should be met from the funds available with the Department of Social Justice.
e) Public Works Department Government Decision No.BDG 2017 / Q.No.60 / Buildings-2, D. Action should be taken under 07.07.2017.
f) Tender instructions for the work should be published by certifying that the planned site is in the possession of the consumer department.
2. Attached is the Recapitulation Sheet submitted as per the scrutiny done by the Public Works Department, Mantralaya, Mumbai.

3. Expenditure on Demand No. Expenditure under head N-4, headings 4225-Capital expenditure on welfare of SCs, STs and OBCs, 277-Education, Scheme under Five Year Plan-Scheme under State Schemes, (01) (03) Construction of Government Hostel for Backward Class Boys and Girls (4225 0481), 53- Major constructions to be met from the budgetary provision made in the financial year 2025-26.
4. Commissioner, Social Welfare, Pune as the Controlling Officer under the said Scheme b. Assistant Commissioner,
Social Welfare, Kolhapur is being declared as the Drawing and Disbursing Officer.
5. Present Government Decisions of the High Level Committee of Secretaries headed by the Chief Secretary.
d. As per the approval received in the meetings held on 28.10.2025 as well as the Financial Rights Manual 1978, Part-
First, Provisions under paragraphs under the Maharashtra Public Works Rules Book under sub-section-V.
Subject to the powers conferred on the Administrative Departments by the foregoing provisions in the Act,
is being released.
This Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
